overview.en: Single-Collateral Dai (Sai) is generated by users of MakerDAO who lock ETH as collateral. Since the release of Multi-Collateral Dai on November 18th 2019, the former Dai has been renamed to Sai and deprecated.
overview.zh: 单抵押 Dai（Sai）是由超额抵押以太币发行，Maker 已经在 11 月 18 日发布多抵押 Dai，并将单抵押 Dai 重名为 SAI，单抵押 Dai 会在几个月后关闭，请在 DApp 浏览器搜索并打开「DAI 升级」，将 单抵押 Dai （Sai）升级为多抵押 Dai，升级完成后即可享有存款利率。
